Ruang kontrolnya Papa.

1678
01:54:46.083 --> 01:54:48.207
Ini. Sini!

1679
01:54:48.208 --> 01:54:49.957
Ini, lihat.

1680
01:54:49.958 --> 01:54:51.290
Coba. Halo?

1681
01:54:51.291 --> 01:54:53.499
Halo, Mama?

1682
01:54:53.500 --> 01:54:56.082
